{
  "section_id": "16-mi355x-vs-mi325x-vs-mi300x",
  "title": "MI355X vs MI325X vs MI300X",
  "title_translation": "MI355X、MI325X 与 MI300X 对比",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "p000",
      "index": 0,
      "source": "On AMD SKUs, we see up to 10x better performance on the MI355X vs the MI300X. AMD has only gotten DeepSeek SGLang Disaggregated Inferencing to work on the MI355X so far AMD has not submitted MI300X or MI325X disaggregated inferencing results, potentially due to software issues on older SKUs that are still being solved.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0199",
      "parent_block_index": 199,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "On AMD SKUs, we see up to 10x better performance on the MI355X vs the MI300X. AMD has only gotten DeepSeek SGLang Disaggregated Inferencing to work on the MI355X so far AMD has not submitted MI300X or MI325X disaggregated inferencing results, potentially due to software issues on older SKUs that are still being solved.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "On AMD SKUs, we see up to 10x better performance on the MI355X vs the MI300X. AMD has only gotten DeepSeek SGLang Disaggregated Inferencing to work on the MI355X so far AMD has not submitted MI300X or MI325X disaggregated inferencing results, potentially due to software issues on older SKUs that are still being solved.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
